Package tmp

Class PortInventory

  • java.lang.Object
    • tmp.TMPObject
      • tmp.PortInventory
  • public class PortInventory
extends TMPObject
    Ports hold Commodities that can bought and sold by Merchants. These Commodities are stored in PortInventories.
